trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 代表集合<xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile"></xref>物件。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The OutputCacheProfileCollection allows to centralize the management of the output cache settings used by pages or user controls.
trans-unit.target: OutputCacheProfileCollection 可集中管理的網頁或使用者控制項所使用的輸出快取設定。

trans-unit.source: It allows you to programmatically access and modify the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile> objects it contains.
trans-unit.target: 它可讓您以程式設計方式存取和修改<xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>它所包含的物件。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile> can be applied to a page using the `CacheProfile` attribute of the [@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2) directive.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] ><xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>可以套用至頁面上，使用`CacheProfile`屬性[@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2)指示詞。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>
